metadata.name: Violent explosions
metadata.description:
smoke rose, the position was a mess, and the cries of wounded soldiers could be heard everywhere.



Zhao Zhiguo shook shake the shell to buzz the head, looked up at the strange around everything, a face of incredible.



"Chi Guo get down!" A second lieutenant will stand up to find out the situation of Zhao Zhiguo to the ground.



The heavy shelling around him nearly deafened Zhao Zhiguo, as the shells exploded close to him, sending rubble crashing into his hands.
